long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Shopify menu assistant extension is a powerful extension for Shopify. It allows you to duplicate, export, and import Shopify menus with one click. Take control of your navigation structure and enhance your productivity, allowing you to focus more on growing your business.

## Traits
Duplicate Shopify Navigation / Menu
Export Shopify Navigation / Menu
Import Shopify Navigation / Menu
Copy Shopify Navigation / Menu
Duplicate & Import Shopify Navigation / Menu between multiple or different store

# Data confidentiality
All Operation is processed in your local computer, it never goes through our web server, no one knows what you have discarded.

Questions? Write to us at the email address: 
menu.assistant.com@gmail.com or directly on our site from this link https://menu-assistant.com/contact

# IMPORTANT NOTE:
Shopify Navigation Assistant is in no way in partnership with the official Shopify site. It is an unofficial application which is independently developed and maintained.
